<h1>Duo Verification</h1>

<p>If you have Duo set up correctly, a prompt should appear below:</p>

<div id="duo-target"></div>

<hr>

<p><strong>Debug info (temporary):</strong></p>
<p>DUO_HOST: <%= DUO["DUO_HOST"].inspect %></p>
<p>sig_request present?: <%= @sig_request.present? %></p>

<script src="https://api.duosecurity.com/frame/hosted/Duo-Web-v2.js"></script>
<script>
    Duo.init({
        host: "<%= DUO["DUO_HOST"] %>",
        sig_request: "<%= @sig_request %>",
        post_action: "<%= duo_verify_url %>",
        post_argument: "sig_response"
    });
</script>
